::Feline::

She smiled and went to the hanger bay for a mode of transportation. She 
found a nice two wheeled land scooter.(motocycle)  She started it up and sat 
at the steering bars.  The engine purred and she purred with delight. "Ah, a 
vehicle after my own spark."  She took off towards the IronFist.

She kept a sharp eye out for the other preds and maximals she might 
encounter along the way. Without back up, she'd be on her own.  She checked 
th side bag and found two plasma pistols.  She smiled, "Alone, but not 
unarmed."  She kept her course and would reach the IronFist soon.
